# Large Model Algorithm Expert

## Company Information

- Locations: Xiaomi Beijing, Xiaomi Wuhan

## Salary & Benefits

- Salary Range: 50k-70k RMB/month
- Payment Cycle: 12 months
- Resume Submission: yuanhaozhi0112@qq.com

## Job Description

1. Develop and iteratively optimize solutions using large language models and multi-modal models for scenarios such as intelligent recruitment, AI interviews, intelligent review, AI data analysis, AI meeting assistants, AI office assistants, and smart customer service.
2. Work closely with product and business teams to design reward models and agent frameworks tailored to scenarios, and continuously optimize business workflows and scenario performance using post-training (SFT/DPO/RL, etc.) and RAG methods.
3. Stay up to date with the latest advancements in the large model industry, write papers and technical reports, participate in academic conferences and technical exchanges, and enhance the technical influence of the company and team within the industry.

## Job Requirements

1. Educational background in computer science or related mathematical fields;
2. Excellent programming skills, proficient in Linux, Python, and Pytorch;
3. Familiar with Transformer architecture and fundamental knowledge of large models, able to track the latest technological trends in language and multi-modal models;
4. Experience in post-training, RAG, agent, and data processing is preferred; reinforcement learning training experience is a plus;
5. Experience publishing in top conferences or contributing to well-known open-source projects is preferred;
6. Strong sense of responsibility, proactive, good communication and teamwork skills, and able to drive business implementation actively.
